WEBVTT

00:00:01.150 --> 00:00:04.285
So, I love making tools
and sharing them with people.

00:00:05.118 --> 00:00:06.508
I remember as a child,

00:00:06.532 --> 00:00:09.825
my first tool I built
was actually a microscope

00:00:09.849 --> 00:00:13.521
that I built by stealing lenses
from my brother's eyeglasses.

00:00:14.289 --> 00:00:16.076
He wasn't that thrilled.

00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:18.270
But, you know, maybe
because of that moment,

00:00:18.294 --> 00:00:19.447
30 years later,

00:00:19.471 --> 00:00:21.359
I'm still making microscopes.

00:00:22.359 --> 00:00:25.658
And the reason I built these tools
is for moments like this.

00:00:27.559 --> 00:00:29.979
(Video) Girl: I have
black things in my hair --